title: League
body: I Cant launch league , everytime i double click it it appears the league of legends logo thing and then nothing appears . Anyone have a solution ?

replies.body: It sounds like a setting is blocking the patcher from launching, so you're getting stuck at the logo.  It could also have crashed in the background, so restart your pc just in case.  Otherwise, run through the [permissions](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) guide to fix it up.  Let me know if you have any questions!
